          {
            "text": "This position is from a game sent by one of my subscribers, and it arose out of a Smith-Morra Gambit Accepted. \n\nWhite has a semi-open d-file and open c-file. In this opening, the Nd5 sacrifice to open up the e-file is very common. \n\nHowever, Black has the option of not taking in many scenarios. And that's what you should do: evaluate whether to take or not. ",
